    "Name": "Shara",
    "Details": "Designed as a replacement to the Mithras and Zorya light tanks, the Shara is a 30 ton light tank powered by a 120 rated Fuel Cell with a max speed of 64kph. Armoured with 3.5 tons of Ferro-Fibrous, the Shara is armed with a ProtoMech AC/8 and an LRM-10. A pair of Medium Chemical Lasers and a pair of Machine Guns provide closer ranged fire power. Limited by it's slow speed and relatively short range, the Shara is a defensive tank deployed in second line units throughout the Inner Sphere Occupation Zones.\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Tracked: High traction, agile turning.</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Fuel Cell: Improved vehicle engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n <b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 5/8 Hex: 150/240 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<b>Armor:</b> Armor (C)\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       120     20\n<b>Left</b>          60     20\n<b>Right</b>        60     20\n<b>Rear</b>         50     20\n<b>Turret</b>       94     20\n\n<b>Total</b>      384    100\n",
